    <innernamespace refid="namespaceSTM32Board">STM32Board</innernamespace>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Shared STM32F103 hardware initialisation for <ref refid="namespaceOpenSkyhawk" kindref="compound">OpenSkyhawk</ref> avionics nodes. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Manages the bi-color status LED, DiagSerial, and CAN peripheral configuration — identical on every <ref refid="namespaceOpenSkyhawk" kindref="compound">OpenSkyhawk</ref> STM32F103CBT6 board. All CAN bus operations (send, filter, start) go through CANProtocol.</para>
<para>Fixed hardware (same on every board — no constructor arguments):<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>LED : PB14 (red) + PB15 (green), active HIGH</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>UART : USART1 PA9 TX / PA10 RX @ 115200 (diagnostic tap)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>CAN : SN65HVD230 on PA11 (RX) / PA12 (TX)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="version"><para>0.2.0 </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="copyright"><para>GPL-2.0-only — see Firmware/LICENSE </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
